{"tid":2258701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★柏傲莊 連錄兩宗撻訂　一房戶買家一周損失40萬","createTime":"2020-10-26T09:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T09:02:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1fe7a5d2692195ddd781615a5909ae905c9032","tid":2258701,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201025/397128730402623488985741.jpeg/LVAh6S1VUCoQbd5fgeYrZCK61j0canXWf9HRoX_R0aE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201025%2F397128730402623488985741.jpeg%2FLVAh6S1VUCoQbd5fgeYrZCK61j0canXWf9HRoX_R0aE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=035e59c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新世界發展（0017）與港鐵（0066）旗下的大圍站柏傲莊 I ，上周六、日進行首輪銷售，391伙兩日內沽清，惟新近有買家撻訂離場，據成交紀錄冊顯示，該2A座46樓D室，實用面積350平方呎，屬一房間隔，於上周六（17日）以約824.1萬元成交，呎價23,546元，惟最新顯示，在簽署臨約後，交易未有進展，料該買家撻訂離場，將損失約41.2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n另一個單位為2A座45樓D室，實用面積同為350平方呎，一房間隔，成交價約816萬元，呎價23,314元，同樣遭撻訂，料損失40.8萬元訂金。即發展商合共殺訂82萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/540257/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8A-i-%E9%80%A3%E9%8C%84%E5%85%A9%E5%AE%97%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82-%E4%B8%80%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B140%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F540257%2F%25E6%259F%258F%25E5%2582%25B2%25E8%258E%258A-i-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2592%25BB%25E8%25A8%2582-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B140%25E8%2590%25AC&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=9cde017b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/540257/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8A-i-%E9%80%A3%E9%8C%84%E5%85%A9%E5%AE%97%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%8